# AKFERP.Web — CoreUI admin panel

## Theme reference

**CoreUI Free React Admin Template (MIT)**
- GitHub: https://github.com/coreui/coreui-free-react-admin-template
- Live demo: https://coreui.io/demos/react/free/
- Docs: https://coreui.io/react/docs/
- Components: https://coreui.io/react/docs/components/accordion/
- Icons: https://coreui.io/icons/
- Charts: https://coreui.io/react/docs/components/chart/

When you need a new component pattern (e.g. modal, toast, tabs, accordion, carousel, progress), look it up in the CoreUI docs above and use the `@coreui/react` component — do NOT build custom CSS equivalents.

## Stack

- `@coreui/react`, `@coreui/coreui`, `@coreui/icons`, `@coreui/icons-react`, `@coreui/react-chartjs`, `chart.js`.
- React 18 + React Router 6 + Vite + TypeScript.
- CSS: CoreUI bundled CSS (`@coreui/coreui/dist/css/coreui.min.css`) imported in `src/index.css`. Brand overrides via `--cui-primary`.

## Brand

- ALKHIDMAT primary: `#0059A3` (`--cui-primary`).
- Logo: `/alkhidmat-logo.png` in `AppSidebar` header and auth pages.
- Font: **Roboto** via Google Fonts in `index.html`.

## Layout

- **`DefaultLayout`**: `AppSidebar` + `AppHeader` + `<Outlet />` + `AppFooter`.
- **Auth/error pages** (`/login`, `/signup`, `/404`): full-screen, **outside** `DefaultLayout`.
- Sidebar nav: `src/_nav.tsx` (array of `CNavItem` / `CNavGroup` / `CNavTitle`).
- Breadcrumbs: `AppBreadcrumb.tsx` → `routeNames` map + `EDIT_PATTERNS` for dynamic `:id` routes.

## CRUD page patterns (reference: Employee module)

### List page (`EmployeeListPage`)
- `CCard` > `CCardHeader` (title + Add button) > `CCardBody`.
- Filters toolbar: `CInputGroup` search + `CFormSelect` department/status + page size.
- `CTable` with `CTableHead color="light"`, `CBadge` for status, `CDropdown` for row actions (Edit/Delete).
- `CPagination` with numbered pages.
- `CModal` for delete confirmation.

### Add / Edit form (`EmployeeForm`)
- Shared component, receives `existing?: Employee` prop.
- `CNav variant="tabs"` for multi-section forms (Personal, Job, Address).
- `CTabContent` + `CTabPane` for tab panels.
- `CFormInput`, `CFormSelect`, `CFormTextarea`, `CFormCheck`, `CInputGroup` with icon prefixes.
- `CFormFeedback invalid` for validation messages.
- `CAlert color="success" dismissible` for save confirmation.
- `CCardFooter` for contextual help text.

### Data store
- In-memory store at `src/data/employees.ts` — swap for API calls later.
- `employeeStore.getAll()`, `.getById()`, `.add()`, `.update()`, `.remove()`.

## Routes

| Path | Page | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| `/` | HomePage | Welcome + feature cards |
| `/login` | LoginPage | Full-screen auth |
| `/signup` | SignupPage | Full-screen registration |
| `/404` | NotFoundPage | Error page |
| `/admin/dashboard` | AdminDashboardPage | Stat widgets + charts + table |
| `/admin/records` | AdminTablePage | Generic paginated table |
| `/admin/records/new` | AdminAddFormPage | Generic add form |
| `/admin/employees` | EmployeeListPage | Full CRUD list |
| `/admin/employees/new` | AddEmployeePage | Add employee (tabbed form) |
| `/admin/employees/:id/edit` | EditEmployeePage | Edit employee (tabbed form) |

## When adding a new CRUD module

1. Create types + data store in `src/data/`.
2. Create `ListPage`, `Form`, `AddPage`, `EditPage` in `src/pages/admin/<module>/`.
3. Add routes in `AppRoutes.tsx` under `/admin`.
4. Add nav entries in `src/_nav.tsx`.
5. Add breadcrumb names in `AppBreadcrumb.tsx` `routeNames` + `EDIT_PATTERNS`.
